    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, she\u2019s been such a dream to drive. It\u2019s in really solid shape and has been super well-loved\u2014perfect for someone looking for a reliable daily driver that still looks great on the road. It runs smoothly and is totally ready for its next big adventure with a new owner!",
