    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offering a mechanically sound FD3S Mazda RX-7, a masterpiece of 50/50 weight distribution and lightweight engineering. This example features the sequential twin-turbocharged 13B-REW rotary engine, which pulls strongly through both stages of boost. Power is sent through a crisp 5-speed manual transmission to a factory Torsen limited-slip differential. To address common thermal management issues, the cooling system has been upgraded with an aluminum high-flow radiator. The suspension maintains its legendary precision via double-wishbone architecture with refreshed bushings. While the exterior shows minor road-going patina, the drivetrain integrity is excellent, with compression numbers verified and a vacuum system that remains tight. A quintessential driver\u2019s car for those who prioritize analog feedback and high-RPM performance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.6,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 14
    },
