      "description": "Hey there! I'm parting ways with my trusty ride, and she's been absolutely wonderful to me. She\u2019s in great shape and has plenty of life left for her next adventure! I've always kept up with the maintenance, so you can hit the road with total peace of mind. It\u2019s a fantastic, reliable car that\u2019s just waiting for a new home. Come take a look and see for yourself!",
