    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "Available is a well-sorted 2004 BMW M3 (E46) featuring the high-strung S54 3.2L inline-six engine, renowned for its individual throttle bodies and 8,000 RPM redline. This unit is paired with a Getrag 6-speed manual gearbox and a variable M differential lock for optimal torque distribution. Crucially, the double-VANOS system has been serviced, and the rear subframe has been reinforced to address common chassis fatigue points. The suspension geometry is maintained via refreshed control arms and bushings, providing the precise turn-in and feedback characteristic of the chassis. While the finish displays minor signs of spirited use, the mechanical vitals\u2014including compression and leak-down figures\u2014remain within factory tolerances. A purist-spec driver with all major preventative hurdles cleared.",
